<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PLeid1,D</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="1" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπίωνι τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶ</supplied>ν διαδόχων καὶ ὑποδιοικητῆι 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Πτολεμαίου τῶν ἐν κατοχῇ ὄντων 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐν τῶι με<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γ</supplied>άλωι Σαραπιείωι ἔτος τοῦτο ἑνδέ-

    <lb n="4"/>κατον <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τοῦ καὶ προεστηκότος τῶν ἐν τῶι ἱερῶι</supplied> </del> 

    <lb n="5"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">διδυμῶν</del> ἀπέδωκά σοι τὴν παρὰ τοῦ βασιλέως 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ τῆς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">β</supplied>ασιλ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ί</supplied>σσ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied>ς κεχρηματισμένην τῶν 

    <lb n="7"/>διδυμῶν ἔντευξιν ὑπὲρ τῶν καθηκόντων 

    <lb n="8"/>αὐταῖς κ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>τ᾽ ἐνιαυτὸν καὶ συνέταξας ἀποδοῦναι 

    <lb n="9"/>τὸ τοῦ [<num value="1">α</num>]<num value="8">η</num> καὶ <num value="19">ιθ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> ἔλαιον καὶ κῖκι ἑκάστου 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐνιαυτοῦ ἐλαίου <choice><corr>με</corr><sic><g type="monogram"/></sic></choice><expan><ex cert="high">τρητὴν</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> κίκιος <choice><corr>με</corr><sic><g type="monogram"/></sic></choice><expan><ex cert="high">τρητὴν</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num>. περὶ μὲν οὖν 

    <lb n="11"/>τούτων δοῖ σοι ὁ Σάραπις <add place="supralinear">καὶ ἡ Ἶσις</add> ἐπαφροδισί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ν χάριν μορφὴν 

    <lb n="12"/>πρὸς τὸν βασιλέα καὶ τὴν βασίλισσαν δι᾽ <choice><corr>ἣν</corr><sic>ης</sic></choice> ἔχεις 

    <lb n="13"/>πρὸς τὸ θεῖον ὁσιότητα. προσδεόμενος δ᾽ ἔτι 

    <lb n="14"/>τυχεῖν καὶ ἐν <choice><corr>τούτο<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ι</supplied>ς</corr><sic>τουτος</sic></choice> συνεργείας ἀξιῶ σε, ἐπεὶ 

    <lb n="15"/>προορῶμαι μήποτε χωρισθέντος σου εἰς τοὺς 

    <lb n="16"/>ἄνω τόπους οὐ λάβω<add place="supralinear">σιν αἱ δίδυμαι</add> τὸ τοῦ εἰκοστοῦ ἔτους 

    <lb n="17"/>ἔλαιον καὶ κῖκι, νομίσαντα ὅτι σὺ ἰδίαι χρηματίζεις αὐταῖ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied>, 

    <lb n="18"/>γράψαι Μεννίδει τῶι <choice><corr>ἐπιμελητῇ</corr><sic>επιμελητει</sic></choice> προσαπο-

    <lb n="19"/>δοῦναί μοι καὶ τούτου τοῦ ἔτους <subst><add place="inline">τὸ<add place="supralinear">ν</add></add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">το</del></subst> καθήκοντα 

    <lb n="20"/>ἐλαίου μετρητὴν καὶ κίκιος μετρητὴν 

    <lb n="21"/>μηδὲν ἀντιπεσόντα. σοὶ δὲ γίνοιτο ἀνθ᾽ ὧν 

    <lb n="22"/>πρὸς τὸ θεῖον ὁσίως διάκ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ει</supplied>σαι καὶ τῶν ἱεροδούλων 

    <lb n="23"/>καὶ τῶν ἐν τῶι ἱερῶι πάντων ἀντιλαμβάνηι 

    <lb n="24"/>ἐπαφροδισία χάρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ις</supplied> μορφὴ <choice><corr>εὐημερία</corr><sic>ευημεριια</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="25"/>καὶ ἐν τοῖς ἄ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">λλοις εὐ</supplied>τυχία. 
<milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/>
    <lb n="26"/>εὐτύχει. 

    <lb n="27"/><handShift new="m2"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τοῖς</unclear> <expan><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>[ρ<ex cert="high">αμματεῦσιν</ex></expan>. <expan>ἐπ<ex cert="high">ισκεψαμένους</ex></expan> <expan>ἀν<ex cert="high">ενεγκεῖν</ex></expan>. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="20">κ</num>] Χοίαχ <num value="23">κγ</num>. 

    <lb n="28"/><handShift new="m3"/> Δωρ[ίωνι. <expan>ἐπι<ex cert="high">σκεψάμενον</ex></expan> <expan>ἀν<ex cert="high">ενεγκεῖν</ex></expan>. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="20">κ</num> Χ]οίαχ <num value="29">κθ</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="2" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="29"/><handShift new="m4"/> Δωρίων. 

    <lb n="30"/>ἐν τῆι γραφῆι τῶν εἰς τὰ 

    <lb n="31"/>ἱερὰ <choice><corr>ὑπόκειται</corr><sic>υποκιται</sic></choice> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del> 

    <lb n="32"/>δίδοσθαι διδύμαις 

    <lb n="33"/>ταῖς ἐν τῶι μεγάλωι Σαρα-

    <lb n="34"/>πιείωι τιμῆς <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">τι</del> τῆς 

    <lb n="35"/><choice><corr>ὑποκειμένης</corr><sic>υποκιμενης</sic></choice> ἐλαίου 

    <lb n="36"/>σησαμίνου <expan>χ<ex cert="high">οῦς</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num>, τοῦ 

    <lb n="37"/>δὲ ἐνιαυτοῦ μετρητὴς <num value="1">α</num>. 

    <lb n="38"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="20">κ</num> Χοίακ <num value="29">κθ</num>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0161-01-23" type="textDate">vor 23. Jan. 161 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Duplikate: UPZ I 33, 34 und 35.</p></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 28.38: <date type="mentioned" value="-0161-01-29">29. Jan. 161 v.Chr.</date></p><p>Z. 9: <date notAfter="-0163" notBefore="-0164" type="mentioned">164 - 163 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">36</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">3427</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">36</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0245;1;36" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">P.Leid. I, Tab. II 1-5</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Boswinkel - Sijpesteijn, Greek Papyri, 5</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.3427" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere